title: FT: Mordecai Brown Portrait - EL Principe De Gales
author: DerekMichael

posts.post_title: FT: Mordecai Brown Portrait - EL Principe De Gales
posts.post_content:
Hello Net54 Patrons. I have a T206 Mordecai Brown Portrait: El Principe De Gales back available for trade. 

Please note that SGC does not slab cards were the name has been cut off. This is their policy, which I was previously unaware of. From what I can tell, the no name is not a result of any alteration, but a result of the factory cut. However, I will leave that to the experts.

Anyways, if anyone thinks that this would fit into their collection, I would be interested in a trade. I collect T206 Hall Of Fame Players and cool tobacco backs. Give me a holler if you would like to try a trade.

Thank You Very Much.

Derek

Mordecai now has a new home. Thank you very much Net54.

Derek
